casebody.data:
Pender C. CATES, Jr.
v.
Peter BUCHOLTZ, Administrator No. 443P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 9, 2019 Pender C. Cates, Jr., for Cates, Pender C. (Jr.) Teresa M. Postell, Assistant Attorney General, Joseph L. Hyde, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 18th of December 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Richmond County:

"Dismissed without prejudice by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of January 2019."
